# Epic 3: Core URL & Group Management with Basic Iframe Display

## Problem Analysis

- **Goal**: Enable administrators to create, manage, and organize URLs and URL Groups. Enable authenticated users to view their assigned groups/URLs. Implement basic iframe display functionality with appropriate visual indicators and navigation.
- **Key Requirements**:
  - Define core content and access database schemas
  - Create admin APIs for URL and Group management
  - Build admin UIs for managing URLs and Groups
  - Implement user-facing API for personalized content
  - Create global UI components (header, user menu)
  - Build dashboard with iframe display capability

## Current Status

