  - API endpoints for URL and Group management are implemented
  - API for fetching user-accessible content is completed
  - AppHeader component with user menu implemented
  - Dashboard with multi-iframe handling implemented
- What's not:
  - Admin UI for URL and Group management still needs to be implemented
- Blocking issues: None at this stage
- Next actions: Implement admin UI components for URL and Group management
- Documentation updates needed:
  - [x] Database schema documentation for content entities
